-- Daimler's Mercedes-Benz Recalls 11,739 Cars in Japan on Steering Wheels
-- B y   T a k u   K a t o
-- 2010-11-16T05:09:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-16/daimler-s-mercedes-benz-recalls-11-739-cars-in-japan-on-steering-wheels.html
Daimler AG’s Mercedes-Benz recalled
11,739 vehicles in Japan because of a problem with the cars’
steering wheels, according to a filing today with the nation’s
transport ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
